1. *Vrhu* planine se nalazi stara pećina. (At the top of the mountain there is an old cave.)
2. On je bio na *vrhu* svoje karijere. (He was at the peak of his career.)
3. Ona je planirala da se popne na *vrhu* planine. (She planned to climb to the top of the mountain.)
4. *Vrhunac* njegovog uspeha je bio nagrada koja je dobio. (The peak of his success was the award he received.)
5. Njihov odnos je dostigao *vrhu* tokom prošle godine. (Their relationship reached the top last year.)